 undocumented infection facilitates the rapid dissemination of novel coronavirus (COVID-19) |year=2020 |last1=Li |first1=Ruiyun |last2=Pei |first2=Sen |last3=Chen |first3=Bin |last4=Song |first4=Yimeng |last5=Zhang |first5=Tao |last6=Yang |first6=Wan |last7=Shaman |first7=Jeffrey |journal=[[MedRxiv]] |type=Preprint |pages=2020.02.14.20023127}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Fl4VA\">{{Cite journal |url=https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.02.17.20024075v1 |doi=10.1101/2020.02.17.20024075 |title=Estimating number of global importations of COVID-19 from Wuhan, risk of transmission outside mainland China and COVID-19 introduction index between countries outside mainland China |year=2020 |last1=Sun |first1=Haoyang |last2=Dickens |first2=Borame Lee |last3=Chen |first3=Mark |last4=Cook |first4=Alex Richard |last5=Clapham |first5=Hannah Eleanor |journal=[[MedRxiv]] |type=Preprint |pages=2020.02.17.20024075}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"qgiV1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/who-china-joint-mission-on-covid-19-final-report.pdf|title=Report of the WHO-China Joint Mission on Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) (Report). World Health Organization. 2020.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"2w5Oj\">{{cite web |url=https://www.zeit.de/wissen/gesundheit/2020-03/christian-drosten-coronavirus-pandemic-germany-virologist-charite/seite-4 |title=Interview with Christian Drosten: \"We Have To Bring Down the Number of Cases Now. Otherwise We Won't Be Able To Handle It\" |date=21 March 2020 |website=[[Die Zeit]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"J1db8\">{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/health/coronavirus-herd-immunity-uk-nhs-outbreak-pandemic-government-a9399101.html |title=60% of UK population need to get coronavirus so country can build 'herd immunity', chief scientist says |date=13 March 2020 |website=The Independent |access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JLWR2\">{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-51835856 |title=Up to 70% of Germ