 pneumonia virus hospitalized in Thailand\u2014the first case outside China |url=https://www.statnews.com/2020/01/13/woman-with-novel-pneumonia-virus-hospitalized-in-thailand-the-first-case-outside-china/ |accessdate=30 March 2020 |work=[[Stat News]] |date=13 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=KuoJanuary21>{{cite news |last1=Kuo |first1=Lily |title=China confirms human-to-human transmission of coronavirus |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jan/20/coronavirus-spreads-to-beijing-as-china-confirms-new-cases |accessdate=30 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]] |date=21 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=AFPJanuary27>{{cite news |title=WHO says global risk of China virus is 'high' |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/world/2020/01/27/who-says-global-risk-of-china-virus-is-039high039 |accessdate=30 March 2020 |agency=[[Agence France Presse]] |date=27 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=KennedyJanuary30>{{cite news |last1=Kennedy |first1=Merrit |title=WHO Declares Coronavirus Outbreak A Global Health Emergency |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/01/30/798894428/who-declares-coronavirus-outbreak-a-global-health-emergency |accessdate=30 March 2020 |work=[[NPR]] |date=30 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=KyodoFebruary29>{{cite news |title=WHO raises global risk from coronavirus to highest level |url=https://english.kyodonews.net/news/2020/02/aa7bacd5ebc5-update1-who-raises-global-risk-from-coronavirus-to-very-high.html |accessdate=30 March 2020 |work=[[Kyodo News]] |date=29 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NPR-20200327\">{{cite news |last=Feng |first=Emily |title=Mystery In Wuhan: Recovered Coronavirus Patients Test Negative ... Then Positive |url=https://www.npr.org/sections/goatsandsoda/2020/03/27/822407626/mystery-in-wuhan-recovered-coronavirus-patients-test-negative-then-positive |date=27 March 2020 |work=[[NPR News]] |accessdate=27 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NYT-20200326\">{{cite news |last=McNeil, Jr. |first=Donald G. |title=The U.S. Now Lead